-- ICBC to Offer Taiwan Companies Additional Credit, Commercial Times Reports
-- Weiyi Lim
-- 2010-06-17T23:15:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/icbc-to-offer-taiwan-companies-additional-credit-commercial-times-reports.html

          
          
             Industrial & Commercial Bank of 
China Ltd. plans to offer Taiwan companies an additional credit
line of $7.5 billion, the Commercial Times reported, citing 
President Yang Kaisheng.  
